high_descs: Turn right into the bedroom to reach the bed.
Pick up the bowl from the bed.
Turn left to walk to the dresser.
Put the bowl on the dresser.
Turn around to exit the room and turn left to walk to the shelf under the tvstand.
Pick up the bowl from the top of the shelf.
Walk to the passage and turn left to the end of the passage and turn right to reach the dresser on the left.
Put the bowl on the dresser to the right of the other bowl.
anns.task_desc: Put two bowls on the dresser.

high_descs: Go forward. Cross to the right. Enter the room, opposite the bed. Get closer to the bed.
Take the soup bowl.
Turn left. Continue ahead. Cross to the right at the end of the dresser. Go ahead, turn left.
Place the soup bowl on the left side of the dresser.
Leave the room. Turn left. To the tvstand. Turn left. Move to the short side of the tvstand.
Take the soup bowl.
Return to the dresser.
Place the soup bowl next to the dresser.
anns.task_desc: Find two soup bowls and place them on top of a dresser.

high_descs: Go straight and turn right and enter into the bed.
Take the bowl from the bed.
Turn left, take a walk and turn right and head towards a cabin
Put the bowl on the top of the dresser.
Turn back and walk few steps again take a right turn to go out of the bedroom. Enter into the left side room and head towards the tvstand.
Take the bowl from the t.v stand.
Then come out of the room, then turn right and enter into the bedroom and head towards the dresser.
Put the bowl next to the dresser.
anns.task_desc: Put the bowls on the top of the dresser
